txt.en: Completed many missions throughout the Ikorbân Valley, assisting the peoples of Shagâna.
Your efforts have truly assisted those who work to improve the fortunes of the Ikorbân Valley. You will be rewarded for your efforts.
'We must continue to forge a new path for all of the peoples of the Ikorbân Valley!\n\n'If you are willing to lend your efforts several more times, I will be able to reward your accomplishments.'
Your aid is requested in the continued efforts to help forge a new path for the peoples of the Ikorbân Valley.
Forging a Path in the Ikorbân Valley (Weekly)
Complete missions throughout the Ikorbân Valley. Missions can be found in Iridír in Ambarûl, Urmâkh in Imhûlar, and Ub Nishir in Urash Dâr.
